    <h1>Air Pollution: A Growing Concern</h1>
    
    <p>Air pollution is one of the biggest environmental challenges we face today. It affects our health, the environment, and the climate. In this blog, we will explore the causes, effects, and potential solutions to air pollution.</p>
    
